Class ResizeableArrayBag<E>

java.lang.Object
ResizeableArrayBag<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
BagInterface<E>
public class ResizeableArrayBag<E> extends Object implements BagInterface<E>
This is the ResizeableArrayBag class which implements the BagInterface interface. With this class, we can create Bags (unordered lists which allow duplicates), find the union, intersection, and difference of two bags. Each method is documented separately.
Version:
3.0
Author:
George Matta
